column4: Ericsson and Cisco in network partnership to boost sales
column5: STOCKHOLM Mobile equipment maker Ericsson and U.S. networking company Cisco Systems Inc said on Monday they had agreed a business and technology partnership that should generate additional revenues of $1 billion for each company by 2018.

column4: Ericsson and Cisco in network partnership  eye sales of $1 bln by 2018
column5: STOCKHOLM  Nov 9 Sweden's mobile equipment maker Ericsson and U.S.  networking company Cisco Systems Inc < CSC.O> said on Monday they had agreed a business and technology partnership expected to generate revenues of $1 billion for each company by 2018.
